The paper deals with the topological analysis of structures used to study maps on data, which involves concepts from computational geometry (cs.CG), data structures (cs.DS), and topology (cs.SI, cs.GT). The paper also discusses the use of metrics and convergence results, which are relevant to information theory (cs.IT).
